Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:16.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, she's a shy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:19.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She makes you want to cheer her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:22.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:23.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:26.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:29.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, she's pretty creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:31.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She {\i1}looks{\i0} creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:32.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks{\i0}, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:36.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:37.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:41.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Written “breezy child,” Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, everyone's afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, even her name is Sadako, like from Ringu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:58.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her parents gave her a pretty blunt name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:55.26,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could just fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:07.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:18.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun is the exact opposite of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:24.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone flocks around him and forms a clique.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:27.70,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,At the opening ceremony when I came to high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:33.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:41.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're heading to Kitahoro High School, it's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.70,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,People only ever apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:53.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But he smiled and thanked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:59.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become like him someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The popular kid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya is, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:13.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unpopular Sawako, on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:21.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka sat in Sadako's seat and stayed home sick for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:23.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:33.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will happen if you sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:40.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any psychic aura or anything either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.91,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Seating change, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:54.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can become good friends with the person next to me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,There's Kazehaya-kun.{T: what's up with the image corruption at the end of this line? Just my aegisub, or the source?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:05.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It sort of sucks that I have no one to share my joy and sadness with at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 19, switch with me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, I'm next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida, your draw—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks, don't need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:48.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:57.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so glad I got this seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:04.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy, from the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:14.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm filled with feelings that I never even knew of, until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hold on to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like the first gifts of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—good for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should learn from Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:40.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She finally fits in with her class, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:43.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it didn't last.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:47.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you who told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's saying so,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:59.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that she's using Kazehaya and you two to up her status.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:02.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you made some friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:05.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san and Yoshida-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:16.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those black rumors about Yano and Yoshida are really something though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Black rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:21.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Backing me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they were down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:27.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They were hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sadako's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because she's wandering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:39.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's going to become seriously worthless too, if he keeps getting followed around by Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:45.27,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1415)}My fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:51.46,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to hurt them again if I stay near them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:53.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're such nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:07:04.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be able to stop the rumors,\Nbut I don't know how to make them feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:09.82,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to go back to what it was like,\Nbefore I got used to being around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:14.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That has to be the best thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:22.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be surprised how positive-thinking she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors and misunderstandings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:32.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now who do you think is the most frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:36.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hate me, why are you avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:45.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:50.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:57.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were being awkward because of the rumors about Yano and Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it were the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:10.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Yano or I avoided you, thinking we'd ruin your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd want to stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:22.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be how they're feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's all about how the other person feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:33.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,His simple words, his smiles... they always nudge me forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good man. He's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:48.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on, don't ruin the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:53.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the love story though, what happens next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:55.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son's going to be sad if he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:08:59.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean up, clean up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:05.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya was watching her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:10.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave her confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:12.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has to make use of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to get off my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:27.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the hell—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:29.72,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:32.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:37.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:42.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how kind they were to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:53.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I more than just like them... I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1050)}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:08.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still sticking up for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after all those rumors she spread?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our problem, so piss off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:32.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be friends with you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:50.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know? We adore you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:57.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming friends happens before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:11:02.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were already friends, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:07.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,We were?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:15.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My first friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sort of worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:24.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka's really liked Kazehaya since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:32.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:40.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making such a racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:43.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he's going to hate you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:58.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There've been lots of rumors about Sadako lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:02.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember seeing her with Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:07.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're going out? Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:18.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can imagine him liking her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:25.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, you're in the sports day committee too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:27.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:28.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:31.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That album I lent you before the last one—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:39.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, what were you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:43.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That CD before the one I lent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:46.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll bring it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan this time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was after Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:29.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:46.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, when the pass comes this way, you go straight—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:02.77,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a new friend again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:08.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, it's not like I put in any effort, so I don't know what to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:16.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:26.24,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is what it's like to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:32.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't really hit me, but I still feel happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:35.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:36.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:41.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You old geezers don't know how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:49.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been watching someone the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:57.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there's someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:01.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:05.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya is the one I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:14.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there going to be someone special for Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:18.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help make that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:20.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:43.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cheer for you honestly, so I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:48.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Kazehaya-kun is special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean special?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he was nice to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:55.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he talked to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he was kind to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just volunteer work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:06.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't even have to be Kazehaya, as long as they're nice to you, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kurumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:15.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what she was trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:19.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan grew up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:21.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She turned her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:24.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now she's taking note of Kazehaya, because of Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:31.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this what it means to like someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:47.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling I have towards Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:53.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:17:00.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:07.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized, we can talk about love together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:15.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rumor from in the washroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:25.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, it was Kurumi that made you suffer so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:32.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought of you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:40.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to tell Kazehaya about me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:47.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him to feel sorry for you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:59.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako wins in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:08.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think Sawako felt better after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:14.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think she wanted to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:27.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:31.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually. Romantically.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:36.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:41.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I came here to tell you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:45.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:50.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you're in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:53.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always with Kazehaya,\N and you don't even have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:56.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:19:00.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could win against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:09.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a lot more in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:20.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're cuter now than when I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:24.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:29.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:36.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know he doesn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:42.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been watching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:54.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:20:00.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make myself think of anyone else more than her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:10.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you at least a little happy that I confessed to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:17.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:28.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They both have the same feelings towards the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:33.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:38.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by any crazy fluke things work out between you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate any woman that Kazehaya likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be friends, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:57.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:08.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:13.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, sake for the cleansing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:30.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:33.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Places that I'll remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Weekend
